  "description": "You need to follow this process if you're registering as a childminder with Ofsted. You don't need to do this if you're registering with an agency. The process is different if you're in Wales, Scotland or Northern Ireland.",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must register with Ofsted or a childminder agency if you want to be paid to look after children under 8 for more than 2 hours a day in England.</p><p>The process to register can take from 4 to 12 weeks.</p>\n"
